All Classes

Class Description
AutoShowroom
The AutoShowroom class have 2 edu.monash.fit2099.vehicles which are Sedan and Truck.
AutoShowroomDriver
The AutoShowroomDriver is the main class of entire program
Bid
The Bid class is for buyer to add Bid based on vehicleID, buyerID, Bid price and date
BidException
The BidException class is used for Bid class to catch any edu.monash.fit2099.exceptions
BidsManager
The BidsManager class is used to store the buyer and bid into a HashMap
Buyer
The Buyer class is used to create a new Buyer based on the buyerID, buyer's given name and last name
IAutoShowroom
An interface(contract) for autoShowroom
Sedan
The Sedan class is for user to add new Sedan based on Sedan's maker, model and seats
SedanException
The SedanException class is used for Sedan class to catch any edu.monash.fit2099.exceptions
Truck
The Truck class is for user to add new Truck based on Truck's maker, model, capacity and wheels
TruckException
The TruckException class is used for Truck class to catch any edu.monash.fit2099.exceptions
Vehicle
The abstract Vehicle class is the parent class of Sedan and Truck
VehicleException
The VehicleException class is the parent class of TruckException and SedanException
